><br/></p><section style=\"font-size: medium; white-space: normal; widows: 1; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(114, 112, 113); font-size: 15px; line-height: 2em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">六个步骤让你永远不用说两遍</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(114, 112, 113); font-size: 15px; line-height: 2em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">六个步骤，一开始看起来似乎很烦琐，但是随着你练习的深入，所需的步骤将会越来越少，因为孩子会越来越快地配合，而通常，就只用前三步孩子就配合家长了</span></p></section></section></section></section><section style=\"font-size: medium; white-space: normal; widows: 1; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 