nt-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">让父母对同一个问题的理解截然不同。</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">父母的思维将影响孩子的前途，</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">对照表格看看，</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">你的思维方式是不是塑造了孩子呢？</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">思维决定命运，思维决定心态，思维决定教育方式，思维影响孩子的前途。一个人在原生家庭中继承和熏陶的最重要的是思维方式。</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(114, 112, 113); font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://yqyd-image.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/201702212833355.jpg\" title=\"null\"/></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 25.6px; fon