e=\"null\"/></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(114, 112, 113); font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><br/></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">看到这里，</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">你还扬得起那双打孩子的手吗？</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">也许打孩子对于我们而言，只是一种教育方式，或是一种情绪的宣泄。但我们永远都不会知道，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(237, 125, 49); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那一幕幕可怕的经历会给孩子年幼的心灵和未来漫长的人生带来怎样的伤害和影响。</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在这部短片中，两个小剧场的脚下放着宣传卡，当一个围观者被吸引，从脚下拿走一张宣传卡的时候，剧场中的暴力嘎然而止，时间仿佛凝固了。</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">随着越来越多的围观者驻足，一张接一张的卡片被传送，家庭暴力剧场也停止不动。</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">视频通过这样一种特别的形式，表达出每个人都是生活中的一员，家庭暴力不是忍受或者看看就能忽视。</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">父母子女，本是骨肉相连，又何必拳脚相向。自古没有打出来的状元，也没有骂出来的榜眼。</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">每一次潮汐都有它的时辰，每一朵花儿都有它的花期，为了不辜负春的美好。</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">请从今天起，不再面目狰狞，你且温暖如春，他自向阳绽放。</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); fo