lor: rgb(114, 112, 113); font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 20.48px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">今天已经初八了，2017年春节过去一半了！春节，我们年年过，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 32px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">但作为现代人的我们，知道咱们的祖辈是如何过年的么？<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">小编这里把中国人过年的传统习俗找全了。</span></span></p></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; widows: 1; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-ratio=\"1.7730496453900708\" data-src=\"http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V143blr